-- Reuters expects Thomson deal to close in April
-- 
-- Tue Feb 19, 2008 10:50am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/19/us-reuters-thomson-close-idUSWLB741420080219

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Reuters RTR.L expects Thomson's TOC.TO acquisition of the London-based financial news and data company to close in the week of April 13. 

 Canadian electronic publisher Thomson and Reuters said in a statement following conditional approval of the transaction by European and U.S. regulators on Tuesday that they will now seek shareholder and court approvals. (Reporting by Gavin Haycock; editing by  Alexander Smith )